author: Cleo Abram
description:
You’re about to see a SUPERMOON…

Supermoons only happen a few times per year and they always occur consecutively. You might have spotted one in October and we’re about to see a few more. 

But what really IS a supermoon and what causes it? Here’s when you can catch the next ones!

If you believe there should be more optimistic science and tech stories, subscribe!

#shorts #Science #space #moon #astronomy
title: A Supermoon Is Coming!
